Main risk: Vehicles travel over the speed limit
Description: I have experience vehicles doing in excess of 20-30km/h over the speed limit consistently. More than 70% of people who use the road speed along the street. There is no 50 km/h signs on Vines Avenue despite its volume of traffic more than doubling in the past 5 years. The government refuses to erect signage on the Road.
